author: muttapodimass
text:
They have every type of meat you could ever want.

The price is a bit higher than you'd expect for what you receive.

Ambience won't take you to china, but will give you the vibe of an Indian Chinese.

Good customer service, nice staff, but food takes long to reach table.

author: muttapodimass
text:
A few days back, we visited this Chinese restaurant in Ooty called Shinkows, looking for something different to eat in Ooty, we stumbled upon this restaurant.

The fried rice and noodles were typical Chinese, and the chicken was extremely tender. https://t.co/cbw1e8ZME9
